26#pragma once
27
28#if ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
29
30#include "ApplicationManifest.h"
31#include "CachedResource.h"
32
33namespace WebCore {
34
35class Document;
36class TextResourceDecoder;
37
38class CachedApplicationManifest final : public CachedResource {
39public:
40 CachedApplicationManifest(CachedResourceRequest&&, PAL::SessionID, const CookieJar*);
41
42 std::optional<struct ApplicationManifest> process(const URL& manifestURL, const URL& documentURL, Document* = nullptr);
43
44private:
45 void finishLoading(SharedBuffer*, const NetworkLoadMetrics&) override;
46 const TextResourceDecoder* textResourceDecoder() const override { return m_decoder.ptr(); }
47 void setEncoding(const String&) override;
48 String encoding() const override;
49
50 Ref<TextResourceDecoder> m_decoder;
51 std::optional<String> m_text;
52};
53
54} // namespace WebCore
55
56SPECIALIZE_TYPE_TRAITS_CACHED_RESOURCE(CachedApplicationManifest, CachedResource::Type::ApplicationManifest)
57
58#endif // ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
